    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cauliflower is golden, remove the dish[es] from the oven, flip the steak[s] over and give the potatoes a good mix up</p><p>Pour the <strong>cheese sauce </strong>all over</p><p>Return the dish[es] to the oven for a further 12-15 min or until bubbling and thickened – this is your <strong>all-in-one creamy cauliflower cheese</strong></p>",
