    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>cauliflower leaves</strong> to a separate baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for 5-8 min or until crispy</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> to the<strong> salad </strong>and drizzle<strong> </strong>over your<strong> red wine vinegar </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your<strong> dressed salad</strong></p>",
